  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Comment: 'Every System should have both a singleton refering to its own class,
    as well as a BaseSystem MonoBehaviour to put data into.


    Then, Reign should
    contain a list of all systems a way to ''get'' them using the name typed into
    the BaseSystem.'
